    "detail": "We were really tired when we arrived from Alishan to Tainan, was quite upset that we did not get to explore tainan at it's full potential. There's a market just located beside the hotel for breakfast options, Tainan does not have much shopping available compared to Chaiyi or Kaohsiung. However we do recommened to stop by Hayashi Department Store -> then 5mins walk to reach Xiao Du Noodle. We missed Da Dong night market because our legs were killing us :( But we do recommend whoever is reading this to do so! We heard great things about it :)",
